name: Tetra - Completion (2/2)
description:
As the last girder was bolted into place, a palpable hum emanated from beneath the surface.  My skin warmed, despite the desperate chill in the air.  I never felt cold again.

Oscilloscope Art - XY oscilloscope trace of custom designed audio sample.  Modern data fed into obsolete tech.
30 second loop.  60fps.
